  • Overrides PouchDbStorageProvider.constructor

    • Defined in runtime/storage/pouchdb/pouch-db-collection.ts:31

    Create a new PouchDbCollection.

    Parameters

    • type: Type

      the underlying type for this collection.

    • storageEngine: PouchDbStorage

      a reference back to the PouchDbStorage, used for baseStorageKey calls.

    • name: string

      appears unused.

    • id: string

      see base class.

      the storage key for this collection.

Private getModelAndUpdate

  • getModelAndUpdate(modelMutator: CrdtCollectionModelMutator): Promise<CrdtCollectionModel>
    • Defined in runtime/storage/pouchdb/pouch-db-collection.ts:334

    Provides a way to apply changes to the model in a way that will result in the crdt being written to the underlying PouchDB.

    • A new entry is stored if it doesn't exist.
    • If the existing entry is available it is fetched and the internal state is updated.
    • A copy of the CRDT model is passed to the modelMutator, which may change it.
    • If the model is mutated by modelMutator, write a new revision and update the local cached copy.

    Parameters

    • modelMutator: CrdtCollectionModelMutator

      allows for modifying a copy of the underlying crdt model.

    Returns Promise<CrdtCollectionModel>
